---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import CyberpunkHero from "../components/CyberpunkHero.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="灰雨电台 - 后朋克夜城档案"
  description="一个关于后朋克、雨夜屋顶和冷色城市回声的虚构站点。"
>
  <main class="page-shell">
    <CyberpunkHero />

    <section class="surface-brief" aria-label="电台状态">
      <div class="brief-track">
        <div>
          <span>频段</span>
          <strong>03:17 / 雨声未停</strong>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span>位置</span>
          <strong>旧楼天台 / 北侧风口</strong>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span>声场</span>
          <strong>低频 / 混响 / 电流底噪</strong>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span>状态</span>
          <strong>无人值守播放</strong>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="about" class="content-section about-section">
      <div class="section-shell about-grid">
        <div class="section-copy">
          <p class="section-label">宣言 / 冷光频段</p>
          <h2>我们不追逐霓虹，只记录霓虹熄灭后的余光。</h2>
          <p>
            灰雨电台是一个虚构的夜间频段，收集后朋克、废墟城市、屋顶风声和二次元边缘感之间的碎片。
          </p>
          <p>
            这里没有明亮的广告牌，也没有胜利的倒计时。只有潮湿墙面、失真的贝斯线、远处闪烁的窗光，以及还没被整理成答案的情绪。
          </p>

          <div class="process-strip" aria-label="播放结构">
            <span>噪声</span>
            <span>回声</span>
            <span>余像</span>
          </div>

          <div class="tool-cloud" aria-label="情绪标签">
            <span>后朋克</span>
            <span>雨夜屋顶</span>
            <span>冷色城市</span>
            <span>失真低频</span>
            <span>废墟浪漫</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <aside class="profile-stack" aria-label="频道参数">
          <div class="profile-visual" aria-hidden="true">
            <span class="profile-core"></span>
            <span class="profile-ring profile-ring-a"></span>
            <span class="profile-ring profile-ring-b"></span>
          </div>

          <div class="signal-panel">
            <div class="signal-row">
              <span>主色</span>
              <strong>蓝黑 / 雾灰 / 暗紫</strong>
            </div>
            <div class="signal-row">
              <span>节拍</span>
              <strong>缓慢 / 重复 / 克制</strong>
            </div>
            <div class="signal-row">
              <span>画面</span>
              <strong>天台 / 雨幕 / 远城</strong>
            </div>
            <div class="signal-row">
              <span>温度</span>
              <strong>低温，仍有窗光</strong>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="availability-card">
            <span>今晚播送</span>
            <strong>旧磁带采样 / 城市雨声 / 未命名现场录音</strong>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="works" class="content-section works-section">
      <div class="section-shell">
        <div class="section-heading">
          <p class="section-label">现场 / 三段夜间记录</p>
          <h2>来自城市边缘的三段低光现场。</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="works-grid">
          <article class="work-card work-card-large">
            <div class="work-visual work-visual-a" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div class="work-meta">
              <p class="work-index">01 / 雨中</p>
              <span>屋顶</span>
            </div>
            <h3>天台回声排练</h3>
            <p>凌晨三点的开放屋顶，鼓机从防水布下面漏出，贝斯线被雨幕切成断续的信号。</p>
            <div class="work-tags">
              <span>湿冷</span>
              <span>低频</span>
              <span>天线</span>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="work-card">
            <div class="work-visual work-visual-b" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div class="work-meta">
              <p class="work-index">02 / 断讯</p>
              <span>地下</span>
            </div>
            <h3>地下通道合成器</h3>
            <p>废弃商业街的卷帘门后，合成器只保留两个和弦，像一盏快要熄灭的蓝色灯。</p>
            <div class="work-tags">
              <span>回授</span>
              <span>暗巷</span>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="work-card">
            <div class="work-visual work-visual-c" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div class="work-meta">
              <p class="work-index">03 / 余温</p>
              <span>远城</span>
            </div>
            <h3>高架桥下的窗光</h3>
            <p>列车经过后，水面短暂发亮。那些黄色窗口像幸存的鼓点，不响，却一直在。</p>
            <div class="work-tags">
              <span>远景</span>
              <span>微光</span>
            </div>
          </article>

        </div>

        <div class="works-note">
          <span>现场说明</span>
          <p>
            这些不是正式演出，更像被雨水保存下来的片段。音量不高，边缘很重，适合一个人站在楼顶听。
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="blog" class="content-section blog-section">
      <div class="section-shell blog-layout">
        <div class="section-heading">
          <p class="section-label">档案 / 雨夜短记</p>
          <h2>几条从旧硬盘里恢复的文字轨道。</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="post-list">
          <article class="post-row">
            <time datetime="2026-05-29">2026.05.29</time>
            <div>
              <p class="post-tag">动效</p>
              <h3>雨丝的速度不能太快</h3>
              <p>如果雨落得像子弹，城市会变成游戏画面。真正的夜晚更慢，也更难解释。</p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="post-row">
            <time datetime="2026-05-28">2026.05.28</time>
            <div>
              <p class="post-tag">过程</p>
              <h3>不要把霓虹开到最大</h3>
              <p>后朋克的城市不需要满屏高饱和。更重要的是黑暗里的轮廓，以及偶尔亮起的窗口。</p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="post-row">
            <time datetime="2026-05-25">2026.05.25</time>
            <div>
              <p class="post-tag">色彩</p>
              <h3>废墟不等于毁灭</h3>
              <p>有些楼只是停止营业，有些人只是停止说话。城市还在呼吸，只是声音变低了。</p>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>

        <aside class="reading-card" aria-label="档案说明">
          <span>档案口径</span>
          <p>只记录低亮度的东西：雨声、楼顶、旧电台、远处的窗光，以及那些没有被白天收编的情绪。</p>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="contact" class="content-section contact-section">
      <div class="section-shell contact-grid">
        <div class="section-copy">
          <p class="section-label">联络 / 无人接线</p>
          <h2>如果你也在雨夜里收听，可以留下一个微弱信号。</h2>
          <p>
            频道不保证立刻回复。它通常在凌晨醒来，在天亮前把消息藏进城市的底噪里。
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-panel">
          <a href="mailto:hello@example.com">
            暂停接收投稿
          </a>
          <a href="https://github.com/524290569-debug" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">
            旧天线 / 公开仓库
          </a>
          <a href="#home">返回雨夜入口</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="site-footer">
      <div class="footer-inner">
        <span>灰雨电台 / 后朋克夜城档案</span>
        <span>东八区 / 雨声循环播放</span>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
